Feature: 1.11 Quality Assurance
As an COP's approver
I carry out a QA on the installation

Background: Given I am logged into a work order
	And I have received the notification for Quality assurance
	Then I can finalise the order

	Scenario: Successful Quality Assurance
		Given I have uploaded the correct information
		When  I approve the work order
		Then  I have finalised the work order

	Scenario: Un-successful Quality Assurance
		Given I have Not uploaded the correct information
		When  I decline the work order
		Then  a notification is sent to the field engineer